author: @santohiji6117
text:
QUICK QUESTION
Why nwjns decides not make appearance in shows like weekly idol, knowing bros, or running man?
They are shows that many international fans knows and helped many groups get famous. I always thought HYBE SCHEDULING system was the reason but then illit make appearance in weekly idol even knowing bros. Even groups like lesserafim, Ive, aespa, gidle, and even their senior BTS made an appearance there. I won't believe reason nwjns didn't get INVITATION by these shows. Nwjns are famous and doing well but it doesn't stop older gen group that also as famous to appear in these shows. I won't believe the reason was they are super BUSY because even the old gen who also as famous as them, perhaps even more, could make it, even ones from their own companies like illit, lesserafim, and even BTS. I won't believe reason their VARIETY SKILL is bad because they look just fine in their own variety show, nothing to worry about their speaking skills. I won't believe they CHOSE NOT TO appear in this shows because despite these shows quite changes (knowing bros format quite change, rm games no longer as active and fun as it's used to, and weekly idol games are repetitive, and their ratings aren't doing really well) these shows were quite legend to boost up fame and even tho nwjns famous, It doesn't hurt to possibly get more and these shows are still fun to watch. I won't believe the reason is fear of RATING impact because even if numbers affect them, nwjns own variety show didn't really reach a fantastic and constant level of view either and it feels like a cowardice move to scared of low rating instead of believing you can make a hit and increase each other fame. I won't believe the reason is MONEY because older groups can meet agreement about money which was why they could appear in these shows and even if one side is being greed, they both lose quite an opportunity there which so regrettable. I won't believe they fear of the CONTENT because I believe these shows have level of fabrication, everything can be scripted and previewed so they can still protect themselves and they are quite a pro in maintain their image.
So why nwjns already being treated like a group that reach elite point and didnt make aopeance  in shows like these and choose to start make their own variety show already?? I get it if they are group like bts, blackpink, or twice that reached their peak of fame, even went beyond, and stopped appearing in these shows at one point so they start make their own. But why nwjns didn't start out like these other groups?? It feels premature!! It makes me suspicious that it was all ADOR MANAGEMENT the reason they didn't make appearance and I'm waiting to see if CEO change will change this.
